result:
<a-modal
  :width="modalWidth"
  :visible="visible"
  title="部门搜索"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="handleSubmit"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭"
  wrapClassName="ant-modal-cust-warp"
  >
  <!--部门树-->
  <template>
    <a-form :form="form">
    <a-form-item :labelCol="labelCol" :wrapperCol="wrapperCol" label="上级部门">
    <a-tree
      multiple
      treeCheckable="tree"
      checkable
      :checkedKeys="checkedKeys"
      allowClear="true"
      :checkStrictly="true"
      @check="onCheck"
      :dropdownStyle="{maxHeight:'200px',overflow:'auto'}"
      :treeData="departTree"
      placeholder="请选择上级部门"
      >
    </a-tree>
    </a-form-item>
    </a-form>
  </template>
</a-modal>
